msgstr "Discovery-endpoint"

#: models.py:72
msgid ""
"URL of your provider discovery endpoint ending with a slash (`.well-"
"known/...` will be added automatically). If this is provided, the remaining "
"endpoints can be omitted, as they will be derived from this endpoint."
msgstr ""
"URL naar de discovery-endpoint van je identity provider. (`.well-known/...`"
"wordt hier automatisch aan toegevoegd). Wanneer deze waarde opgegeven is, "
"dan kan je de overige endpoint-velden leeg laten omdat ze automatisch gevuld "
"zullen worden."

#: models.py:80
msgid "JSON Web Key Set endpoint"
msgstr "JSON Web Key Set-endpoint"

#: models.py:83
msgid ""
"URL of your provider JSON Web Key Set endpoint. Required if `RS256` is used "
"as signing algorithm."
msgstr ""
"URL naar de endpoint waar de JSON Web Key Sets te vinden zijn. Deze is verplicht "
"als het ondertekenalgoritme `RS256` is."

#: models.py:89
msgid "Authorization endpoint"
msgstr "Autorisatie-endpoint"

